# CASE MANAGEMENT ARCHITECTURE

The Case Management module is the heart of LCAA.

Every legal activity inside the platform revolves around a Case.

A Case is not only a folder.

A Case is a living digital entity.

Each Case contains its own documents, evidence, events, notes, actions, timeline and AI analysis.

